# Build context for the web image is apps/. Keep host-installed deps and local
# env files out so the in-image pnpm install is authoritative and Vite config
# arrives only via build args (ARG -> ENV in web/Dockerfile).
#
# pnpm symlinks node_modules into a version-specific content-addressed store;
# copying the host's over the in-image install produces dangling symlinks.
**/node_modules

# Build caches / incremental TS state are host-specific.
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.tmp

# .env must not shadow the build args (absent in CI anyway).
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Note: ui-core/dist is intentionally NOT ignored — it is the prebuilt library
# artifact that web resolves @ssv/ui-core to.
